snippet.title: Spider-Man 2 - PSP Longplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Name: Spider-Man 2

Description: Scale New Heights. You are Spider-Man-slinging webs, scaling walls and performing innovative combos in an attempt to protect New York from the dangerous deeds of Doc Ock and other classic villains. Prepare for new scenarios in fully immersive 3D environments unlike anything you've seen in a handheld game.

Release Date: March 2005
